: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2.1 DELIVERY AREAS</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Items offered on our website are only available for delivery to addresses within </span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">{service areas e.g. Klang Valley}</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">. Delivery areas may expand, shrink or change depending on weather and traffic conditions and situations of force majeure.&nbsp;</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2.2 DELIVERY TIME</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">We shall deliver your Order to the delivery address provided by you. You may choose for your Order to be delivered or scheduled for a specific time slot. Delivery times shall vary depending on factors that are not controlled by us (e.g. order quantity, distance, time of day (peak periods), weather conditions, traffic conditions, etc.).</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2.3 NO-SHOW CANCELLATIONS</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">If you remain uncontactable or fail to receive the Order within ten (10) minutes from the time the Order arrives at your delivery address, we reserve the right to cancel the Order without refund or remedy to you. Second attempt delivery will not be attempted unless requested and delivery fee will be charged separately.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2.4 ORDER PICK-UP</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2.4.1 Where available, you will have the option of collecting your Order in-person directly from our premises (“Pick-Up”) instead of having the Order delivered to You. You will be notified the time for you to Pick-Up the Order (“Collection Time”). We will prepare the Order by the Collection Time. In some cases, a reasonable delay may be expected.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2.4.2 In the event of unreasonable delays in Pick-Up attributable to you, you bear the risk of any damage or loss of Items or any deterioration in quality or change in condition of the Items (e.g. changes in the temperature fit for consumption). In this case, you shall not be entitled to a replacement, refund or replacement of the Items/Order. You alone are responsible for inspecting the Items/Order when you Pick-Up your Order and shall report any issues and/or defects to us before leaving our premises.</span></p><p><br></p>',
